HEADWORD: Showroom
<hw>Show"room`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A room or apartment
where a show is exhibited.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A room where merchandise is exposed for sale, or
where samples are displayed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Showy</ent>⟦br⟧
